Install:
claude mcp add --transport http memesio https://memesio.com/api/mcp

Config:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "memesio": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "https://memesio.com/api/mcp"
    }
  }
}

Usage:
claude mcp add --transport http memesio https://memesio.com/api/mcp
claude mcp list
claude mcp status memesio
